ludes 2,000 contacts, unlimited email sends, full automation sequences, sales funnels, and a CRM. It replaces Klaviyo's core functionality at $0/month for most Shopify stores."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How much does Klaviyo cost per month in 2026?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Klaviyo costs $45/month for 500 contacts, $70/month for 1,000 contacts, $175/month for 5,000 contacts, and $350/month for 10,000 contacts. Adding SMS increases the cost further."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What changed with Klaviyo pricing in 2025?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "In February 2025, Klaviyo changed from charging only for contacts you actively email to charging for every active profile \u2014 any contact who has engaged or been added in the past 90 days. Shopify stores with large customer bases saw immediate bill increases."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can I migrate from Klaviyo to Systeme.io?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Export your Klaviyo subscriber list as a CSV, import into Systeme.io, and rebuild your key automations (welcome sequence, abandoned cart, post-purchase). Stack Architect's Replace Klaviyo Free guide covers the complete migration in under 30 minutes."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Does Systeme.io work with Shopify?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Systeme.io integrates with Shopify via Make.com webhooks or Zapier. When a customer places an order, Shopify fires a webhook that adds them to Systeme.io and triggers your post-purchase automation sequence. No code required."}}]}]})}/>
